Interface FRootElement

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier

    public interface FRootElement
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject
    A representation of the model object 'FRoot Element'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Pools
    • Lanes
    • Processes
    • Participants
